long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
JSView for Chrome. View JS and CSS files.
This extension displays included JS and CSS files in the context menu.
By clicking on a file, it opens in a new tab.

Inspired by the great JSView extension for Mozilla Firefox.
